## 七、完整 HTML 模板

```html
<div class="pagination">

  <!-- 左侧：total + page size -->
  <div class="pagination-left">
    Total 128 entries,
    <select class="page-size-select">
      <option>10/page</option>
      <option>20/page</option>
      <option>50/page</option>
    </select>
  </div>

  <!-- 右侧：导航 + Go to page（全部在右侧） -->
  <div class="pagination-right">
    <button class="page-btn nav">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
    </button>
    <button class="page-btn">1</button>
    <button class="page-btn">2</button>
    <button class="page-btn">3</button>
    <button class="page-btn active">4</button>
    <button class="page-btn">5</button>
    <button class="page-btn">6</button>
    <button class="page-btn ellipsis">···</button>
    <button class="page-btn">1000</button>
    <button class="page-btn nav">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="page-goto">
      Go to page
      <input class="page-goto-input" type="number" value="4" min="1" />
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
```

